'''John William DiMaggio''' provided the voice of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]] and [[Sha'a Gi]] for [[Clone Wars Chapter 20|Chapter 20]] of the ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]'' cartoon. DiMaggio also voiced the [[bounty hunter]] [[Baash]] in the [[2016]]&ndash;[[2017]] television ''[[LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures]]''. 

==Biography==
John DiMaggio and his co-star [[Danny Jacobs]], who voiced [[Raam]], appeared as guests on ''[[The Star Wars Show]]'' on [[September 20]], [[2017]].<ref name="The Star Wars Show September 22 2017">{{StarWarsShow|ewg2ZpaLsL0|We Unearth Super Rare Star Wars Toys, Talk with John DiMaggio and Danny Jacobs, and More!}}</ref>

